{
  "stem": "15943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were a few children that were born in Russia or they were in hiding, [? so the-- ?] of kindergarten age, four or five years old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The rest are just children that were born in '46 or-- or '47.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I had pleasure in teaching them to sing Yiddish songs, and to clap hands, to see them smile.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto I-- I wasn't a kindergarten teacher in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this-- I don't know what the title over there was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My former kindergarten teacher, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Musta, ?] had in the ghetto formed a kindergarten-- hold on-- held on to the children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she had ask me, as one of her children, which was now, you know, older, to come and work with her, would help her there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was kind of experienced-- put it this way-- to work with-- with children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't think you needed much experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You just needed love.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because all those children needed is love, to feel secure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "July 7, 1949.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was born in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leffeld, ?] because Leipheim was being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's why we always moved from place to place, because they were liquidating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was born July 7 in [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leffeld. ?] And at that time, we were hoping to be able to go to America.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So between red tapes and medical problems, he was born there, rather than being born in the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were waiting to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, we waited five years [SIGHS] to find-- first, we had to find a sponsor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We found a sponsor through a sheer miracles, because we did-- had no addresses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we didn't have anything to prove our relations or who we are.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
